Package: rp.flm.test
Type: Package
Title: Goodness-of-fit Test for the Functional Linear Model with Scalar Response Based on Random Projections
Version: 0.0.6
Date: 2019-09-25
Authors@R: c(person("Eduardo", "García-Portugués", role = c("aut", "cre"),
		     email = "edgarcia@est-econ.uc3m.es"), person("Manuel", "Febrero-Bande", role = "aut", email = "manuel.febrero@usc.es"))
Description: Goodness-of-fit test for the functional linear model with scalar response based on random projections. The package implements the method described in Cuesta-Albertos, García-Portugués, Febrero-Bande and González-Manteiga (2019) <doi.org/10.1214/18-AOS1693>.
